\pard \fs26\sl360\slmult1\tx187\tx360\tx547\tx720\tx907\tx1080\tx1267\tx1440\tx1627\tx2160\tx1987\tx2160\tx2347\tx-1436\tx2707\tx2880\tx3067\tx-1436\tx3427\tx-1435\tx3787\tx-1435\tx4147\tx4320\tx4507\tx-1435\tx4867\tx5040\tx5227 
{\plain \fs26 \fs26 \par
}{\plain \fs26 \fs26 To amend Title 50 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to state government, \softline
so as to comprehensively revise the provisions of law regarding open meetings and open \softline
records; to provide definitions relating to open meetings; to provide for the manner of closing \softline
meetings; to provide for open meetings; to provide for remedies for improperly closing \softline
meetings; to provide for notice of meetings; to provide for exceptions; to provide for certain \softline
privileges; to provide for sanctions; to provide for related matters; to provide for legislative \softline
intent regarding open records; to provide for definitions relating to open records; to provide \softline
for applicability; to provide for procedures regarding disclosure and enforcement of \softline
disclosure provisions; to provide for fees and the amount and manner of collection thereof; \softline
to provide for exceptions and exemptions; to provide for sanctions; to provide for related \softline
matters; to conform certain cross references; to provide for an effective date and \softline
applicability; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.\par
}{\plain \fs26 \fs26 \par
}\pard \fs26\qc\sl360\slmult1\tx187\tx360\tx547\tx720\tx907\tx1080\tx1267\tx1440\tx1627\tx2160\tx1987\tx2160\tx2347\tx-1436\tx2707\tx2880\tx3067\tx-1436\tx3427\tx-1435\tx3787\tx-1435\tx4147\tx4320\tx4507\tx-1435\tx4867\tx5040\tx5227 
