the purpose of making photographs or reproductions of the same while in the possession, \softline
custody, and control of the lawful custodian thereof, or his authorized deputy. Such work \softline
shall be done under the supervision of the lawful custodian of the records, who shall have \softline
the right to adopt and enforce reasonable rules governing the work. The work shall be done \softline
in the room where the records, documents, or instruments are kept by law. While the work \softline
is in progress, the custodian may charge the person making the photographs or \softline
reproductions of the records, documents, or instruments at a rate of compensation to be \softline
agreed upon by the person making the photographs and the custodian for his services or the \softline
services of a deputy in supervising the work.}{\plain \fs26 \fs26 \par
}\pard \fs26\li547\sl360\slmult1\tx187\tx360\tx547\tx720\tx907\tx1080\tx1267\tx1440\tx1627\tx2160\tx1987\tx2160\tx2347\tx-1436\tx2707\tx2880\tx3067\tx-1436\tx3427\tx-1435\tx3787\tx-1435\tx4147\tx4320\tx4507\tx-1435\tx4867\tx5040\tx5227 
{\plain \fs26 \fs26 (b)}{\plain \fs26 \ul\fs26 (1)(A)  Agencies shall produce for inspection all records responsive to a request \softline
within a reasonable amount of time not to exceed three business days of receipt of a \softline
request; provided, however, that nothing in this chapter shall require agencies to \softline
produce records in response to a request if such records did not exist at the time of the \softline
request.  In those instances where some, but not all, records are available within three \softline
business days, an agency shall make available within that period those records that can \softline
be located and produced.  In any instance where records are unavailable within three \softline
business days of receipt of the request, and responsive records exist, the agency shall, \softline
within such time period, provide the requester with a description of such records and \softline
a timeline for when the records will be available for inspection or copying and provide \softline
the responsive records or access thereto as soon as practicable.}{\plain \fs26 \fs26  }{\plain \fs26 \strike\fs26 Where fees for certified \softline
